data.description: Welcome to your charming new home in Memphis, TX! This delightful 3 bedroom, 2-bathroom residence has undergone remodeling and updates, making it the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic appeal.  As you arrive, you'll appreciate the convenience of a spacious carport, ensuring your vehicles stay protected from the elements year-round. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior boasting a fresh and inviting atmosphere. The open-concept living and dining areas are bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance for gatherings with family and friends. One of the standout features of this property is the expansive backyard, adorned with mature trees that offer shade and privacy. This is the perfect backdrop for outdoor activities, from relaxation to gardening or playtime. Additionally, sheds in the backyard and carport provide extra storage space for your tool and equipment. This home is a place where cherished memories will be created, take a look today
